Writing Data to External Storage
You can save DataFrames to various formats and storage systems.

Step 1: Write DataFrame to CSV
Scala:

scala
 
scala>  DF.write.option("header", "true"). ("path/to/save/ ")
Python:

 
 
>>>  DF.write.option("header", "true"). ("path/to/save/ ")
Step 2: Write DataFrame to Parquet
Scala:

scala
 
scala>  DF.write.parquet("path/to/save/parquet")
Python:

 
 
>>>  DF.write.parquet("path/to/save/parquet")
